{"tid":405980,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量]感恩日記(1)","createTime":"2017-09-19T09:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T08:08:42.000Z","uid":139272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"907c92889927262abfb0036cee9fabded6f6f39b","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"愈感恩，愈能夠吸引到同頻既事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由今日起，試下連續30日記錄低自己遇到既好人好事<br />\n30日後，睇下自己生活有咩變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只專注討論好人好事，持續放大正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎大家加入，一齊分享自己遇到既好人好事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n祝福各位巴絲日日都充滿正能量!<br />\n<br />\n9月19日 (第一日)<br />\n<br />\n今朝要返工，但我幾乎唔知醒<br />\n好彩屋企人及時走過黎叫醒自己<br />\n仲要見我咁趕，整埋早餐比我食完去返工<br />\n好彩最後都趕得切返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超級窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慶幸身邊有咁好既屋企人，好感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca29e379c3e9ecd419f77b8bdd5cbcd7ed579ad","tid":405980,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"完。"},{"pid":"3363359c808faf46f936a1b3e5857c1befc0a17b","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"連登正能量系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5e244863a8e8ebc623c29bed457a13702c5417","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105a3a715e5c438aa854f3761db3a7e3efd03329","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"我會堅持寫落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83505a231708d0e7dcc96036142f2b8546051ed2","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f148dc2bb08352e0c46b1108d566f9c2b9550126","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家加入，一齊分享自己遇到既好人好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90247b49efb7fbdfcf11514bf2c4118962112aa0","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd88e8481a9090b99d74966584b786dcc7cd6db","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2174adaee3665665d59cbc51a9dbb0340abc2ee8","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"祝福各位巴絲日日都充滿正能量!<br />\n<br />\n9月20日 (第二日)<br />\n<br />\n平時夜晚不嬲都成兩三點訓教<br />\n成日搞到朝朝起身番工勁趕<br />\n但琴日太攰勁早就訓左(十二點半)<br />\n訓左成七個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝起身非常準時<br />\n仲要好少可朝早會咁精神<br />\n訓得夠，心情都好似輕鬆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落到樓下仲要唔洗點等就上到巴士<br />\n返到office早成半個鐘添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感恩今日有個精神既身軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c06d1de2c5f0f3c6aac34846da198ccc1fe392f","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4e8143de14d7ca4696ab4fde3c42f104ea80d9","tid":405980,"uid":136924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5026e8be4be69943ab844c336c2019b58bbb88","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你，我會堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd4678a3971ef98087a39921c14f3050308f8be","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8697e611550dd7bff7115408b6534ed3ecceec3b","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d872cfced448ef18c67b6c9f990c3f8fcc5806b0","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:08:06.000Z","msg":"9月21日 (第三日)<br />\n<br />\n今日食lunch既時候<br />\n本身諗住去開平時食果間<br />\n但後尾又想試下新野<br />\n咁就行左去第度食啦<br />\n結果去到一間餐廳<br />\n點知發現呢間野又真係幾好食<br />\n仲要少有地37蚊包飯包野飲<br />\n最重要坐得夠舒服又唔逼<br />\n睇怕黎緊日日都會去果間食晏<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日都無咩特別事值得自己感恩<br />\n但起碼都係一件小小既開心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5d6849a475624b211c54ba72959b0c6381190f","tid":405980,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:08:42.000Z","msg":"繼續發放正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}